{"tid":1554882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈要求成立獨立調查委員會傳召羅範椒芬","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:00:40.000Z","uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5deaaf978bd1af849bde35c17429b038fc1ffbb6","tid":1554882,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"反對《逃犯條例》爭議仍尚未平息，警民衝突無日無之。行政會議成員羅范椒芬今天（9日）早上接受香港電台英文台節目《Backchat》，稱有年輕少女為一些勇士（Warriors）提供免費性愛，又指已確認真有其事（I think we have confirmed that this is a true case.）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嘩嘩嘩<br />\n咁嚴重呀<br />\n咁一定要成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n第一時間傳召呢條八婆<br />\n查清查楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下佢點解會confirm到<br />\n我諗除咗接觸過作案人士之外都好難confirm呀<br />\n<br />\n邊個反對成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n就即係縱容性暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fbd1060d7c9cb8131d9b254ace17c14d7dd4c4","tid":1554882,"uid":289623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:00:40.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}